  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective observational clinical multicentric study in ICU with acute renal
      failure requiring renal replacement therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Prospective before / after observational clinical multicentric study on ICU acute kidney
      injury during renal replacement therapy. Evaluation of incidence and exposure to hemofilter
      clotting.

      The after phase will consist in medical measures (help for prescription) and paramedical
      measures (stop the filtration flow during the patient's mobilization).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
